title: Schuele Boys Gang associate gets 10-month prison term
text:
Published By: Buffalow News: City - Today 
Ikeem Lyons, 22, an associate of the Schuele Boys Gang of East Side drug dealers, was ordered to serve a 10-month federal prison term Friday...
